text: Macaranga mauritiana is a species of plant in the family Euphorbiaceae. It is endemic to Mauritius. ==References== mauritiana Category:Endemic flora of Mauritius Category:Endangered plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Plants described in 1866 Category:Taxa named by Wenceslas Bojer Category:Taxa named by Henri Ernest Baillon
